      • open

        public void open(Window window)
        Description copied from interface: Setup
        Opens a window to a player. This window will be automatically maximized and if the player already has a maximized window, the current window will be minimized. The current window will be maximized, if the player closes the new window. The window, witch will be minimized, will get the Status.BACKGROUND. If you do not want, that the current window will be maximized on closing the new window, invoke Setup.minimize() before opening the new window. The WindowOpenEvent will be called in the EventManager. To maximize the new window, the method Setup.maximize(Window) will be called.
        Specified by:
        open in interface Setup
        Parameters:
        window - to open

      • close

        public void close(Window window)
        Description copied from interface: Setup
        Closes an open window to a player. The window to close does not has to be in the state Status.MAXIMIZED. All other states are possible too and the window will be closed. If the closing window is the maximized window of the given player the method Setup.minimize() will be called. The WindowCloseEvent will be called in the EventManager.
        Specified by:
        close in interface Setup
        Parameters:
        window - to close

      • maximize

        public void maximize(Window window)
        Description copied from interface: Setup
        Maximizes a window to a player. If a window is currently maximized the current window will get the state Status.BACKGROUND. If the new maximized window gets minimized the first window with the state Status.BACKGROUND will be automatically maximized. The WindowMaximizeEvent will be called in the EventManager.
        Specified by:
        maximize in interface Setup
        Parameters:
        window - to maximize

      • minimize

        public void minimize()
        Description copied from interface: Setup
        Minimizes the currently maximized window. If the player does not have a maximized window this method will do nothing. If the player has any other opened windows with the state Status.BACKGROUND the first window with this state will be maximized with a little delay of one tick. The WindowMinimizeEvent will be called in the EventManager.
        Specified by:
        minimize in interface Setup
